reviews.review_text: Awesome ambiance, delicious food, and a food and fabulous service üòã highly appreciated.  Menu will be customized as per your requirements.

I recently dined at Sher-E-Punjab Restaurant and Bar, and it was a fantastic experience. I tried the Paneer Tikka Masala along with Onion Kulcha and Masala Kulcha, and they were all incredibly tasty! The Paneer Tikka Masala was rich and flavorful, perfectly complemented by the soft and well-prepared kulchas. Whether you're into veg or non-veg, this place has something delicious for everyone. Highly recommended for a satisfying meal!

Excellent resto, will surely come back, reasonable price with authentic north Indian cuisine. Feels like you are really in Punjab ,,one of the best in town. Will bring my parents next visit. Royal falooda was wow. Mutton was so soft and didn't stink. Satisfied. Will try the tandoori next time. Coz it smells so good.

### Sher-E-Punjab Goa: A Culinary Jewel in Goa Velha

This establishment has garnered attention for its delectable **seafood**, scrumptious **kulfi**, and rich **rabdi**, making it a favored spot for both locals and tourists alike.

### Ambiance & Design

![Delicious Food](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdm1u5Dfy3WRrpz_Yx5FBIk7628rziNKJ7tN5ekiTjwChqW5dsa2n-fPnlX63CH83aB0R2qoI823pTpvia7o06MwsGE4sUWbHJaJkds6IoD-2EoTHuFpEUG0gTduM2XvMP2qtiVAeA=w375-h281-p)

### Popularity & Reviews

Sher-E-Punjab has emerged as a beloved culinary destination, particularly among tourists looking to indulge in authentic Indian flavors. The establishment not only attracts positive customer sentiment but also boasts an active social media presence, with photo shares highlighting delectable dishes that keep the buzz alive. Patrons express eagerness to return, often mentioning plans to introduce family members to the experience.

![Seafood Delicacies](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnleUsdt-8qzJdVzrLUpmHnui8jMy9tgmkQqCJDvI5qt97gAWuSEFgeeEeOJSy6FoCFHlLTR3BYVtkp2LY0vJLPeb1shTfvZAyFrFKO_kcZrh-hkHY7mh53FMw_8L5_VF4v1ghS=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In essence, **Sher-E-Punjab** is more than just a restaurant; it's a gastronomic experience that transports diners straight to the heart of Punjab, all while located in the beautiful setting of Goa Velha. With a well-rounded menu featuring everything from **rabdi** to **kulfi**, paired with a welcoming atmosphere and attentive service, it‚Äôs no surprise that this spot ranks highly among local and traveling food enthusiasts alike.
